{"TopicDetails": {"type": 0, "ccm2Id": 44834232, "cftId": 0, "identifier": "ISF-2022-TF1-AG-CORRUPT", "title": "CORRUPT", "publicationDateLong": 1647907200000, "callIdentifier": "ISF-2022-TF1-AG-CORRUPT", "callTitle": "Call for proposals on the fight against corruption", "callccm2Id": 44834247, "allowPartnerSearch": true, "workProgrammepart": {"id": 6234, "ccm_id": 44653690, "wp_part": "ISF-2022", "wp_year": "ISF-2022", "wp_title": "ISF-2022", "wp_website": "https://ec.europa.eu/home-affairs/funding/internal-security-funds/internal-security-fund-2021-2027_en", "wp_document": "https://ec.europa.eu/home-affairs/funding/internal-security-funds/internal-security-fund-2021-2027_en"}, "frameworkProgramme": {"id": 43252368, "abbreviation": "ISF", "description": "Internal Security Fund (ISF)"}, "programmeDivision": [{"id": 44477751, "abbreviation": "ISF-2-1", "description": "Corruption"}], "topicMGAs": [], "tags": ["money laundering", "Law enforcement", "whistle blowers", "corruption", "public procurement"], "sme": false, "actions": [{"status": {"id": 31094503, "abbreviation": "Closed", "description": "Closed"}, "types": [{"typeOfAction": "ISF-PJG ISF Project Grants", "typeOfMGA": [{"id": 43250150, "abbreviation": "ISF-AG", "description": "ISF Action Grant Budget-Based"}]}], "plannedOpeningDate": "22 March 2022", "submissionProcedure": {"id": 31094504, "abbreviation": "single-stage", "description": "single-stage"}, "deadlineDates": ["31 August 2022"]}], "latestInfos": [], "budgetOverviewJSONItem": {"budgetTopicActionMap": {"3393311": [{"action": "ISF-2022-TF1-AG-CORRUPT - ISF-PJG ISF Project Grants", "plannedOpeningDate": "22 March 2022", "deadlineModel": "single-stage", "deadlineDates": ["31 August 2022"], "budgetYearMap": {"2022": 2000000}, "budgetTopicActionMap": {}}]}, "budgetYearsColumns": ["2022"]}, "description": "<SPAN class=\"topicdescriptionkind\">Scope</SPAN>:<p>Call for proposals on fight against corruption</p>\n", "conditions": "<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.4px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\" lang=\"EN-US\">Conditions<br />\r\n</span></b></p>\r\n<p><b><span style=\"color:#404040;mso-themecolor:&#xA;text1;mso-themetint:191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\" lang=\"EN-US\">1.&nbsp;</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Admissibility conditions: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">section 5</a> of the call document</span>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proposal page limits and layout:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described in Part B of the Application Form available in the Submission System. Part B<strong> </strong><u>without<strong> </strong></u>annexes is limited to max 50 pages. List of previous projects to be sublitted as a <u>separate annex</u>. <br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">2. Eligible countries:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">section 6</a> of of the call document</span></p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">3. Other eligibility conditions:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described in <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">section 6</a> of the call document</span></p>\n<p><b>4. Financial and operational capacity and exclusion:&nbsp;</b>described in&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">section 7</a> of the call document</span></p>\n<p><b><span lang=\"FR-BE\">5.&nbsp;Evaluation and award:</span></b></p>\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Award criteria, scoring and thresholds:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described in <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><u>section 9</u></a> of the call document</span></li>\r\n</ul>\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\" lang=\"EN-US\">Submission and evaluation processes</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;described&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">section 8</a> of the call document and the</span>&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/common/guidance/om_en.pdf\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Online Manual</span></a></li>\r\n</ul>\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">Indicative timeline for evaluation and grant agreement:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described in<a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> section 4</a>of the call document</span></li>\r\n</ul>\n<p><b><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\" lang=\"EN-US\">6</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">. Legal and financial set-up of the grants:&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">described&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">in <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/isf/wp-call/2021-2022/call-fiche_isf_2022-tf1-ag-corrupt_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">section 10 </a>of the call document</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.4px; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\" lang=\"EN-US\">Documents<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></